extendedInfo.description: ///After install don't press 'Open', just use your back button. Also, don't use the shortcut icon. Just apply the theme in the GO Keyboard settings./// *You must have GO Keyboard installed to use this theme.With his GO Keyboard theme you can enjoy the look and feel of the computer displays in the new Star Trek movies (2009 and 2013 Into Darkness PCAP style to replace the standard LCARS). This theme is ideal for true fans or anyone who wants a sleek Sci-Fi look. This keyboard theme was designed to accompany the other New Star Trek themes, but will look great by itself.Directions:This is a theme, so after installing don't press 'Open', just 'Done'.ãTo apply the theme, open the menu in GO Keyboard and tap "Theme settings" then "Select theme" then find this theme and apply it. **You must have GO Keyboard installed**Also look for:New Star Trek Go Launcher ThemeNew Star Trek GO Contacts ThemeNew Star Trek Go Locker ThemeNew Star Trek GO KeyboardNew Star Trek GOWidget ThemeNew Star Trek Go SMS ThemeNew Star Trek Live WallpaperNew Star Trek GO FontsNew Star Trek clock & battery skin (available free in Beautiful Widgets theme picker)*clock updated to v2*As you can see, I have a very complete theme pack to customize the whole phone / tablet for all parts of common use.To get informed when I release new Star Trek themes, follow me on twitter. @SethSteen or Facebook http://www.facebook.com/new.star.trek.theme Also, if you're a Trekkie I would appreciate it if you could support my work by clicking 'g+1' or sharing it on your social networks.If you like my work, PLEASE leave me a nice review to help me continue. Too many people never read the directions and leave a bad review saying, "It doesn't work".*If you are having trouble and the contact developer link isn't working, please contact me at seththomaslewis@gmail.com That is my personal email so I can get notifications right away and offer the fastest support.

reviews.title: Fantastic!
reviews.comment: Another top app by Seth the man who can :-). Looks great, works perfectly
reviews.author: Russell Spicer

reviews.title: EXCELLENT
reviews.comment: Another incredible theme from a TRULY TALENTED artist!  Freakin\' AWESOME!! Keep up the EXCELLENT work, my friend.
reviews.author: Mike Diekamp

reviews.title: Fantastic
reviews.comment: Seth has a great eye for details and has the best response time of any developer i have emailed. Just remember if you run jelly bean read the directions and email him if you need to.
reviews.author: Matthew Francis

reviews.title: Awesome!!
reviews.comment: This theme is great. I have all the new Star Trek themes and love them. A must have for any trekkie or anyone wanting a great looking theme.
reviews.author: John Walton

reviews.title: Buy it!
reviews.comment: Im not the type to buy themes, I would either suffer through free ones, or make my own. These themes are amazing, and worth the money IMO. Every time I turn around he seems to have another one done... Looking forward to a Go Weather widget theme (hint hint) ;)
reviews.author: steve corder

reviews.title: Awesome
reviews.comment: I bought this app but it will not load on my S3.  The app support tech contacted me with easy install directions and it works awesome. (Wish there was a provision or compatable app for trek computer typing  \'clicks\' and open/close event effects also?)
reviews.author: Tony Grossart

reviews.title: New Star Trek
reviews.comment: Is there any end to your talent???????  The only ones I haven\'t bought yet are the live wallpaper and I\'m really tempted!  I love the way my phone looks now. You was kind enough to send me some free sound files which I needs to download it through as pc.  Awesome
reviews.author: John Dixon

reviews.title: If you have NST go SMS Pro, keyboard is essential
reviews.comment: The quality, design, authenticity and attention to detail is perfect!  The customer is so responsive, that its almost like have Seth next to you fixing the issue! Once again, cant say enough good about this essential add-on and developer!
reviews.author: spark E-Lohim

reviews.title: get these...
reviews.comment: Great apps! Designer responded quickly and gave efficient instructions for jelly bean compatibility.  High quality.
reviews.author: Joshua Shaffer

reviews.title: Should be easier one day
reviews.comment: This looks great and as a fan of the trek i like it. Sadly its not very easy to get installed but that could change. Id say its worth it. it would be 5 stars if it came with star trek sounds as you typed like on a console on the bridge .
reviews.author: Graham Frost

reviews.title: It worked!
reviews.comment: Yes it worked! I\'m so happy it did! :D thank you! I\'m a big fan of star trek so this is really worth it. <3
reviews.author: Chelymar Miranda

reviews.title: The best
reviews.comment: Customer service is number one. . . This app is AWESOME!!
reviews.author: James Sims

reviews.title: Nice Keyboard
reviews.comment: Love the way this keyboard looks on my phone... I think I pretty much got the whole themes!  it makes my phone look and feel as if I am actually holding a device from star trek itself... awesome... questing though, does the keyboard have any sound effects as you type away??? if it does can you show me how to add that... otherwise... great job...  Live Long and Prosper!
reviews.author: Reina Morris

reviews.title: More Trek Awesomeness!
reviews.comment: Awesome theme from an awesome developer! I started with their Go Launcher Star Trek theme & immediately had to get this & the matching Go SMS Pro theme! Absolutely beautiful & works flawlessly! I definitely want the 3rd live wallpaper & lock screen, too!
reviews.author: Cat M

reviews.title: As always, couldn\'t be better.
reviews.comment: Don\'t take ANYONE\'s word here. Look at the apps, live wallpapers, etc. released by the other huge companies, and compare them yourself. I am a HUGE Star Wars fan, and the available material released by the big names was such a complete joke that I had no interest in disgracing my screen with it.   This developers product is what we all have in mind when we think of future high tech. Exactly what I wanted. THAT\'s talent.
reviews.author: Ameer Nuub

reviews.title: Cool look; well matched to theme
reviews.comment: Easy to use and quite legible. A few futuristic buttons aren\'t immediately obvious, but it\'s easy to learn and remember.  Looks great as part of theme. Patch is easy to take care of.
reviews.author: Dan Robinette

reviews.title: Nice.
reviews.comment: This collection of themes is awesome. You have to read the directions or you\'ll likely screw up the install but it\'s worth the time. Fun to customize the screens and impressed all my nerdy companions.... love it! Worth the money! Also great tech support from Seth!
reviews.author: Amy Wilhite

reviews.title: Awesome
reviews.comment: Not to sound like a broken record, but this add-on theme to the already awesome New Star Trek Theme series is the best! It ties in the whole thing together very beautifully.  And for those trolls who can\'t read the description on how to make it work, and give poor ratings, please, go back to using a flip phone.
reviews.author: Tam Rachatanavin

reviews.title: Droid Razr Maxx user
reviews.comment: Anybody out there that is a Star Trek fan should pick this app up immediately it\'s worth every penny trust me I know, and be advised I will be picking up every other app out there that has to do with this Star Trek theme, because I need it.
reviews.author: Doarmell R Jackson

reviews.title: You found what you were looking for
reviews.comment: Yeah it is everything you are reading here in the comments and then some to put it mildly. Outstanding and full of a lot of features!!!!
